headline: Invesco Canada announces cash distributions for its ETFs
summary: Invesco Canada Ltd. ("Invesco"), a leading global asset management firm, announced today the October 2023 distributions for its exchange-traded funds (ETFs). Unitholders of record on October 30, 2023, will receive cash distributions payable on November 7, 2023.
